          <li>Create your first <a href="https://github.com/FlorianBruniaux/claude-code-ultimate-guide/blob/main/guide/ultimate-guide.md#claudemd-project-instructions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CLAUDE.md</a></li>
          <li>Practice with simple tasks</li>
          <li>Learn <a href="https://github.com/FlorianBruniaux/claude-code-ultimate-guide/blob/main/guide/ultimate-guide.md#diff-review-workflow" target="_blank" rel="noopener">diff review workflow</a></li>
          <li>Explore <a href="https://github.com/FlorianBruniaux/claude-code-ultimate-guide/blob/main/guide/ultimate-guide.md#slash-commands" target="_blank" rel="noopener">slash commands</a></li>
