          <li>Create <a href="https://github.com/FlorianBruniaux/claude-code-ultimate-guide/tree/main/examples/agents" target="_blank" rel="noopener">project-specific agents</a></li>
          <li>Master <a href="https://github.com/FlorianBruniaux/claude-code-ultimate-guide/blob/main/guide/ultimate-guide.md#plan-mode" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Plan Mode</a></li>
