          <h3>DevOps / SRE</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="path-description">Infrastructure and reliability focus</p>
        <ol class="path-steps">
          <li>Setup <a href="https://github.com/FlorianBruniaux/claude-code-ultimate-guide/blob/main/guide/devops-sre.md#quick-self-check" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Claude for infrastructure</a></li>
